name: Add new LiquidPlanner projects to Google Sheets
description: Every time there is a new project in LiquidPlanner, Make will automatically add this project to a specified spreadsheet in Google Sheets. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1lJkP54SAczUlpOWMksnNLGnhfDCSRnvD_qIHkZHSMMg/edit?usp=sharing).
